    "The backbone is composed of a succession of 5 spatiotemporal blocks.",
    "Each spatiotemporal block consists of a temporal convolution followed by a spatial convolution.",
    "The model can be configured to run in streaming inference mode by using an input FIFO buffer for each temporal layer.",
    "The sliding-window mechanism of the FIFO buffer would act as the convolution sliding window, and the convolution operation itself is simply replaced by a dot product between the elements in the FIFO buffer and kernel weights.",
    "C. Compares the methods of direct binning, event volume binning, and causal event volume binning."
